methods.writeTo:
Serializes object into out. Must only be called with a compatible object, see
 ObjectType.isType(Object).

 
 Objects that object references may be serialized as ObjectType.Exporter.Reference.

 
 Note: the implementation should not hold onto references nor create references outside the calling thread.

:param exporter: (io.deephaven.plugin.type.ObjectType.Exporter) - the exporter
:param object: (java.lang.Object) - the (compatible) object
:param out: (java.io.OutputStream) - the output stream
